WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

2
00:00:27.527 --> 00:00:29.363
There's another child in her belly.

3
00:00:29.446 --> 00:00:31.781
I knew it. she's having twins.

4
00:00:33.575 --> 00:00:35.702
It's almost dawn.

5
00:00:35.785 --> 00:00:37.871
Don't give birth yet!

6
00:00:37.954 --> 00:00:41.249
Granny! Don't ask for the impossible.

7
00:00:41.332 --> 00:00:42.375
But she has to!

8
00:00:43.543 --> 00:00:46.087
Even if it's impossible. just do it.

9
00:00:46.796 --> 00:00:52.886
Because these children will be the ones
who command the daemons!

10
00:01:19.162 --> 00:01:22.874
The children who sunder day and night
have been born.

11
00:01:34.219 --> 00:01:38.389
16 YEARS LATER

12
00:02:33.403 --> 00:02:35.446
What a beautiful dragon's fart.

13
00:02:58.469 --> 00:02:59.345
Oi! Yuru!

14
00:02:59.929 --> 00:03:02.933
Have ya gone huntin' alone again?

15
00:03:03.016 --> 00:03:05.351
Yo. Danji. I'm back.

16
00:03:05.852 --> 00:03:08.146
Why didn't ya tell me?

17
00:03:08.229 --> 00:03:09.064
My bad.

18
00:03:09.147 --> 00:03:12.097
What if somethin' happens to ya
all alone in the mountains?

19
00:03:12.734 --> 00:03:14.361
You can't call for help. ya know?

20
00:03:14.444 --> 00:03:15.737
It's fine.

21
00:03:16.321 --> 00:03:18.921
The Divine Guardians Right and Left
will protect me.

22
00:03:21.576 --> 00:03:22.452
Wow!

23
00:03:22.535 --> 00:03:24.454
Ya caught a pheasant!

24
00:03:24.537 --> 00:03:25.455
Wasn't that difficult?

25
00:03:25.538 --> 00:03:26.748
It was easy.

26
00:03:26.831 --> 00:03:29.459
Let's have a grilled bird!
- No. a hot pot.

27
00:03:29.542 --> 00:03:31.628
It tastes and smells better
when it's grilled.

28
00:03:31.711 --> 00:03:33.296
Hot pot is more satisfying.

29
00:03:33.379 --> 00:03:34.380
Yer wrong!

30
00:03:36.466 --> 00:03:38.051
Oh. Yuru! Welcome back.

31
00:03:38.635 --> 00:03:39.469
I'm back.

32
00:03:39.552 --> 00:03:41.802
The weather looks like
it's going to get bad.

33
00:03:42.138 --> 00:03:44.057
Will we finally get some rain?

34
00:03:44.807 --> 00:03:46.309
I'll come help later.

35
00:03:46.392 --> 00:03:47.810
Yeah! Thanks!

36
00:04:04.327 --> 00:04:06.454
Granny Yamaha. I'm back.

37
00:04:06.537 --> 00:04:08.289
Welcome back. Yuru.

38
00:04:08.790 --> 00:04:10.709
Danji. perfect timing.

39
00:04:10.792 --> 00:04:12.586
Oh no. it's Ma!

40
00:04:12.669 --> 00:04:14.629
Come 'ere and help me!

41
00:04:14.712 --> 00:04:16.089
Bye!

42
00:04:16.172 --> 00:04:17.007
Hey!

43
00:04:17.090 --> 00:04:19.842
Learn to be a hard worker like Yuru!

44
00:04:20.343 --> 00:04:21.678
Is Asa well?

45
00:04:21.761 --> 00:04:25.807
She's doing her duty properly as always.

46
00:04:41.698 --> 00:04:42.699
Asa.

47
00:04:44.325 --> 00:04:45.285
How are you?

48
00:04:47.578 --> 00:04:48.830
Welcome back.

49
00:04:49.664 --> 00:04:50.873
Brother.

50
00:04:54.752 --> 00:04:56.379
I caught a pheasant today.

51
00:04:56.462 --> 00:04:58.673
You're amazing. Brother!

52
00:04:58.756 --> 00:05:00.383
Not really.

53
00:05:00.883 --> 00:05:03.553
I wanted to catch a boar or a deer.

54
00:05:04.053 --> 00:05:07.140
There hasn't been much rain this year.
so I'm worried about the harvest.

55
00:05:07.724 --> 00:05:10.226
There might be less food this winter.

56
00:05:10.727 --> 00:05:14.856
I have to hunt more
and make dried or salted meat.

57
00:05:15.356 --> 00:05:20.778
Will the adults of the village leave for
the outside world to find work?

58
00:05:21.362 --> 00:05:22.613
Maybe.

59
00:05:23.865 --> 00:05:25.700
Will you go. too?

60
00:05:25.783 --> 00:05:27.160
I won't!

61
00:05:27.660 --> 00:05:30.413
Why do you think I trained myself to hunt?

62
00:05:31.372 --> 00:05:34.167
If I become indispensable
to the village for hunting.

63
00:05:34.250 --> 00:05:36.627
I won't need to leave.

64
00:05:37.253 --> 00:05:41.925
You won't leave like
Mother and Father did?

65
00:05:42.008 --> 00:05:44.386
Don't worry. Asa.

66
00:05:44.469 --> 00:05:46.721
I'll never leave this village.

67
00:05:47.221 --> 00:05:50.433
As long as you're here.
I'll always be with you.

68
00:05:50.933 --> 00:05:52.143
I'll protect you.

69
00:05:55.605 --> 00:05:56.606
Yeah!

70
00:05:58.441 --> 00:05:59.358
Yuru!

71
00:06:00.818 --> 00:06:01.944
Yes?

72
00:06:03.154 --> 00:06:05.114
Dera is here.

73
00:06:06.157 --> 00:06:08.076
It's good steel.

74
00:06:09.202 --> 00:06:11.496
Here. from the folks who
went to the outside world.

75
00:06:11.579 --> 00:06:13.247
Thanks for always.

76
00:06:13.748 --> 00:06:15.125
How is it out there?

77
00:06:15.208 --> 00:06:17.711
The economy's pretty bad.

78
00:06:17.794 --> 00:06:19.921
There's a pandemic as well.

79
00:06:20.004 --> 00:06:23.007
Which is why. today.
I want to trade with some herbs.

80
00:06:23.674 --> 00:06:25.135
I'll trade this for salt.

81
00:06:25.218 --> 00:06:27.553
Do you have some vegetable seeds
that can grow in drought?

82
00:06:28.179 --> 00:06:29.556
Here you go.

83
00:06:29.639 --> 00:06:32.559
My daughter will soon be seven.

84
00:06:32.642 --> 00:06:33.643
I see.

85
00:06:33.726 --> 00:06:36.104
Then. I'll bring a witch doctor next time.

86
00:06:37.605 --> 00:06:40.316
I got some bad headaches lately.

87
00:06:40.858 --> 00:06:42.308
The usual painkillers. right?

88
00:06:42.860 --> 00:06:44.029
Stomach medicine. please.

89
00:06:44.112 --> 00:06:46.531
Sure!
- Dera.

90
00:06:46.614 --> 00:06:49.075
Oh. Yuru! How are you?

91
00:06:49.617 --> 00:06:50.993
Anything you want?

92
00:06:52.161 --> 00:06:53.371
Not really…

93
00:06:54.539 --> 00:06:58.126
"I don't want anything.
Any souvenirs for Asa?"

94
00:06:58.209 --> 00:06:59.252
Right?

95
00:07:01.629 --> 00:07:02.755
Thanks.

96
00:07:03.256 --> 00:07:06.593
What?! Pheasant feathers? That's great!

97
00:07:06.676 --> 00:07:08.226
I can sell it for a good price.

98
00:07:12.348 --> 00:07:13.599
How lucky.

99
00:07:14.183 --> 00:07:16.769
I wanna leave this village too.

100
00:07:17.270 --> 00:07:19.313
Is the world out there really great?

101
00:07:20.106 --> 00:07:24.277
The folks who left rarely return.

102
00:07:24.819 --> 00:07:27.280
The outside world must be
a pretty good place.

103
00:07:27.363 --> 00:07:29.365
Really?

104
00:07:29.991 --> 00:07:32.702
I wouldn't mind living here my whole life.

105
00:07:33.369 --> 00:07:35.372
Yeah. right.

106
00:07:35.455 --> 00:07:38.541
Ya have a cute younger sister.

107
00:07:39.500 --> 00:07:42.253
Why don't ya leave with yer sister?

108
00:07:42.336 --> 00:07:44.714
If yer worried. I'll come with ya.

109
00:07:44.797 --> 00:07:48.593
Being with you will sully Asa.

110
00:07:48.676 --> 00:07:49.635
What did ya say?!

111
00:07:50.344 --> 00:07:52.430
She has an important duty!

112
00:07:53.014 --> 00:07:56.476
Come to think of it.
I've never met Asa at all.

113
00:07:57.101 --> 00:07:59.062
She can only meet with certain people.

114
00:07:59.145 --> 00:08:02.232
Don't say that. Big Bro.

115
00:08:02.315 --> 00:08:05.693
I won't let a peasant like you meet her.

116
00:08:05.776 --> 00:08:07.237
What?!

117
00:08:07.320 --> 00:08:09.322
Then. fight me first!

118
00:08:09.405 --> 00:08:10.805
No. no. no. I don't want to!

119
00:08:14.660 --> 00:08:15.745
What's this sound?

120
00:08:16.245 --> 00:08:18.164
Isn't it a dragon cry?

121
00:08:18.664 --> 00:08:19.540
Look.

122
00:08:20.291 --> 00:08:22.210
Again. beautiful dragon's fart.

123
00:08:32.803 --> 00:08:35.223
But it's not roaring.

124
00:08:35.306 --> 00:08:37.183
It's different from the usual.

125
00:08:37.850 --> 00:08:41.395
I've heard it many times
when I was hunting in the mountains.

126
00:08:42.104 --> 00:08:43.689
Isn't it getting loud?

127
00:08:44.190 --> 00:08:45.942
Maybe it's close.

128
00:08:46.025 --> 00:08:48.278
Have you ever seen a dragon?

129
00:08:48.361 --> 00:08:49.403
Nope.

130
00:09:12.718 --> 00:09:13.636
Look.

131
00:09:42.999 --> 00:09:44.584
Calm down!

132
00:10:04.520 --> 00:10:06.772
Wha…

133
00:10:18.326 --> 00:10:20.036
Gran! Granny Yamaha!

134
00:10:20.786 --> 00:10:22.121
What is happening?

135
00:10:22.204 --> 00:10:25.583
This is bad. The barrier has been broken.

136
00:10:25.666 --> 00:10:27.001
Just how?!

137
00:10:27.084 --> 00:10:30.129
I don't know.
but their target is probably Yuru.

138
00:10:31.213 --> 00:10:34.300
Anyway. hide him now. Bring him to me!

139
00:10:34.383 --> 00:10:35.217
Yeah!

140
00:10:35.885 --> 00:10:36.928
Where is Yuru?

141
00:10:37.011 --> 00:10:39.263
Probably in the field! Hurry up!

142
00:10:42.892 --> 00:10:44.018
What is happening?

143
00:10:44.769 --> 00:10:46.479
What the heck is happening here?

144
00:10:49.523 --> 00:10:51.359
Everyone was killed.

145
00:10:52.193 --> 00:10:54.028
Stay with me. Danji!

146
00:10:55.154 --> 00:10:57.239
Please live. Ma!

147
00:11:05.414 --> 00:11:06.290
We found him.

148
00:11:08.084 --> 00:11:09.085
Stop!

149
00:11:12.129 --> 00:11:13.423
Something weird just flew here!

150
00:11:13.506 --> 00:11:16.425
I don't know what that is.
but it's pretty destructive.

151
00:11:22.723 --> 00:11:25.184
The dragons are flying around
the outer walls!

152
00:11:25.851 --> 00:11:27.801
I don't think we can win against those.

153
00:11:28.187 --> 00:11:30.337
In the first place.
are those even dragons?

154
00:11:37.029 --> 00:11:41.242
I think Ma is workin'
at the keep like usual.

155
00:11:42.159 --> 00:11:44.662
Yer goin' there too for Asa. right?

156
00:11:45.621 --> 00:11:46.789
Help me. Danji.

157
00:11:47.373 --> 00:11:48.333
What now?

158
00:11:48.416 --> 00:11:49.959
Just help me!

159
00:11:58.467 --> 00:11:59.301
What is this?

160
00:12:00.302 --> 00:12:01.763
Shortcut to the keep.

161
00:12:01.846 --> 00:12:03.848
A shortcut? To the keep?

162
00:12:03.931 --> 00:12:05.850
I never knew about this!

163
00:12:05.933 --> 00:12:06.767
I told you…

164
00:12:07.476 --> 00:12:10.076
The Divine Guardians Right and Left
will protect us.

165
00:12:14.066 --> 00:12:16.235
Asa… Please be safe.

166
00:12:17.903 --> 00:12:19.363
Oi. Yuru!

167
00:12:29.582 --> 00:12:31.542
Hello there.

168
00:12:37.131 --> 00:12:38.090
Gobble.

169
00:12:44.722 --> 00:12:45.931
Gobble.

170
00:12:46.849 --> 00:12:47.933
Gobble. Gobble.

171
00:12:49.268 --> 00:12:50.227
Gobble. Gobble.

172
00:12:53.731 --> 00:12:54.940
Gobble.

173
00:13:05.743 --> 00:13:06.911
Ma…

174
00:13:08.204 --> 00:13:10.206
I won't bite children.

175
00:13:13.375 --> 00:13:14.376
Gobble.

176
00:13:18.047 --> 00:13:20.299
Hello. it's Gabby.

177
00:13:20.799 --> 00:13:23.511
I've taken over
the outer and middle areas.

178
00:13:25.054 --> 00:13:27.932
Ground squad. you can come here.

179
00:13:34.396 --> 00:13:35.648
Hello. ground squad?

180
00:13:37.233 --> 00:13:39.610
Hooo. boy.

181
00:13:39.693 --> 00:13:41.278
What to do now?

182
00:13:43.030 --> 00:13:45.324
The barrier's been broken.

183
00:13:46.742 --> 00:13:50.079
Hello? Hana. hun? It's me.

184
00:13:51.747 --> 00:13:54.458
Since I can contact you. this means bad.

185
00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:56.669
Can you see the smoke from there?

186
00:13:57.336 --> 00:13:58.587
I see.

187
00:13:59.255 --> 00:14:01.382
Can we change our meeting point?

188
00:14:03.467 --> 00:14:04.969
I think…

189
00:14:05.719 --> 00:14:07.179
Asa has come.

190
00:14:21.193 --> 00:14:24.572
So that's how it is.

191
00:14:29.368 --> 00:14:30.494
What a sick joke.

192
00:14:37.126 --> 00:14:38.002
What a sick joke.

193
00:14:58.606 --> 00:14:59.440
Asa!

194
00:15:00.357 --> 00:15:01.191
Yes.

195
00:15:01.692 --> 00:15:03.402
Asa is here. Brother.

196
00:15:03.986 --> 00:15:05.112
I've come to pick you.

197
00:15:06.322 --> 00:15:07.615
And…

198
00:15:09.992 --> 00:15:12.119
I will kill everyone besides you.

199
00:15:13.287 --> 00:15:14.246
What…

200
00:15:15.789 --> 00:15:18.083
What are you talking about?

201
00:15:20.044 --> 00:15:21.670
No way…

202
00:15:22.838 --> 00:15:23.839
Someone like you…

203
00:15:25.090 --> 00:15:27.677
Could be my sister!

204
00:15:27.760 --> 00:15:29.595
Get out of my way!

205
00:15:35.434 --> 00:15:38.812
So they're pretending to
be mountain rescuers.

206
00:15:47.613 --> 00:15:51.283
It'll be a problem if they keep going
along the escape route from above.

207
00:15:57.247 --> 00:15:58.207
Oh dear.

208
00:15:59.124 --> 00:16:01.127
Would you look at that?

209
00:16:01.210 --> 00:16:05.089
What a great set of teeth you have.

210
00:16:07.925 --> 00:16:08.759
Oh!

211
00:16:09.426 --> 00:16:11.762
Are you a Seer. mister?

212
00:16:16.642 --> 00:16:18.019
That's some strong enamel.

213
00:16:18.102 --> 00:16:21.730
Were you the one who eliminated
the ground squad?

214
00:16:33.659 --> 00:16:36.662
Sorry. I only meant to break the arrow.

215
00:16:38.288 --> 00:16:40.082
I'm still not used to this.

216
00:16:59.226 --> 00:17:01.061
Dera! Take Yuru and run!

217
00:17:07.401 --> 00:17:08.736
Hide in the outside world!

218
00:17:09.319 --> 00:17:10.988
Don't let them find him!

219
00:17:11.071 --> 00:17:12.239
Aye. aye!

220
00:17:13.657 --> 00:17:15.117
Ma. are you okay?

221
00:17:17.661 --> 00:17:18.495
Yuru?

222
00:17:19.079 --> 00:17:20.330
Yuru!

223
00:17:43.937 --> 00:17:46.857
Yuru. we'll descend the mountain.

224
00:17:47.858 --> 00:17:50.110
What is going on here?

225
00:17:50.903 --> 00:17:54.198
What is happening. really?

226
00:17:54.281 --> 00:17:55.824
Just follow me for now!

227
00:18:05.167 --> 00:18:07.294
Damn it! Missed our chance.

228
00:18:11.340 --> 00:18:14.718
If the girl with teeth comes.
we'll be trapped.

229
00:18:15.219 --> 00:18:16.303
Asa…

230
00:18:17.721 --> 00:18:19.306
Asa is dead.

231
00:18:20.891 --> 00:18:24.812
Wait. Is she? But she moved.

232
00:18:25.479 --> 00:18:27.481
We left Granny behind.

233
00:18:27.981 --> 00:18:29.733
Who was that woman?

234
00:18:30.484 --> 00:18:32.319
She killed everyone.

235
00:18:32.903 --> 00:18:35.823
Even though no one did anything wrong…

236
00:18:35.906 --> 00:18:38.534
No time to explain.

237
00:18:42.121 --> 00:18:44.039
You gotta use the Right and Left.

238
00:18:44.665 --> 00:18:46.542
Huh? The Divine Guardians?

239
00:18:46.625 --> 00:18:47.875
What do you mean by that?

240
00:18:48.210 --> 00:18:49.294
There.

241
00:18:50.129 --> 00:18:53.090
There's a hole between them.

242
00:18:53.173 --> 00:18:54.341
Put it into the hole.

243
00:18:56.051 --> 00:18:57.928
I don't understand!

244
00:18:58.011 --> 00:18:59.972
It's a present from me!

245
00:19:00.055 --> 00:19:01.807
Pre… what?

246
00:19:01.890 --> 00:19:02.975
Just do it!

247
00:19:03.559 --> 00:19:05.853
You do it. Yuru!

248
00:19:06.395 --> 00:19:08.897
Seriously! What's this all about exactly?!

249
00:19:09.481 --> 00:19:11.817
And no one explains anything!

250
00:19:13.652 --> 00:19:15.821
The hole is filled with trash!
- Dig it!

251
00:19:17.990 --> 00:19:19.492
It's the boy.

252
00:19:19.575 --> 00:19:22.119
Capture him! You can kill the others!

253
00:19:22.202 --> 00:19:24.621
You should've cleaned that up properly!

254
00:19:26.165 --> 00:19:27.833
It's in. Dera!

255
00:19:30.669 --> 00:19:33.380
What was that for. Dera?!

256
00:20:01.116 --> 00:20:02.159
What are those?

257
00:20:37.694 --> 00:20:39.613
No!

258
00:20:42.824 --> 00:20:45.118
My ride home is gone.

259
00:20:45.994 --> 00:20:48.789
I hate walking down the mountain.

260
00:20:51.083 --> 00:20:52.459
Calm down. you two.

261
00:20:53.961 --> 00:20:56.004
Something's appeared.

262
00:20:57.005 --> 00:20:58.882
I wonder whose daemons?

263
00:20:59.841 --> 00:21:02.052
I hope they're weakling.

264
00:21:10.477 --> 00:21:12.729
Good grief.

265
00:21:13.480 --> 00:21:16.275
Our new master is a kid.

266
00:21:17.025 --> 00:21:19.695
He looks easy to get along with. Left.

267
00:21:20.696 --> 00:21:23.449
Be it a child or an adult.

268
00:21:23.532 --> 00:21:27.577
we have to obey our master. Right.

269
00:21:29.371 --> 00:21:32.499
Ghosts. demons. monsters.

270
00:21:32.582 --> 00:21:36.712
UMAs. spirits. pairs…

271
00:21:36.795 --> 00:21:41.550
Well. humans call them with
a lot of different names.

272
00:21:42.426 --> 00:21:46.138
Yuru. they are your daemons.

273
00:21:52.853 --> 00:21:53.895
Daemons?

274
00:22:11.872 --> 00:22:14.875
All the pain I've experienced

275
00:22:18.628 --> 00:22:23.216
Has traveled through my veins

276
00:22:25.343 --> 00:22:28.305
And passed through my heart

277
00:22:32.100 --> 00:22:35.479
By the time I've forgotten. it arrives

278
00:22:35.562 --> 00:22:36.522
In my brain

279
00:22:36.605 --> 00:22:38.607
I guess it's not that bad

280
00:22:38.690 --> 00:22:41.694
But there's this tiny little draft

281
00:22:41.777 --> 00:22:45.781
Of resentment and sadness

282
00:22:45.864 --> 00:22:50.202
Just let me have this

283
00:22:50.285 --> 00:22:53.414
I'm spineless

284
00:22:53.497 --> 00:22:57.084
All my words and tears

285
00:22:57.167 --> 00:23:00.796
And these feathers grown from my feelings

286
00:23:00.879 --> 00:23:03.757
I'll put all of them on my back

287
00:23:03.840 --> 00:23:06.927
Well. see you later

288
00:23:07.010 --> 00:23:10.806
I'll leave it all behind here

289
00:23:10.889 --> 00:23:12.057
I'm not scared

290
00:23:12.140 --> 00:23:14.184
Up in the sky

291
00:23:14.267 --> 00:23:17.104
See these feathers flutter in the wind

292
00:23:17.187 --> 00:23:22.526
And follow along

293
00:23:26.488 --> 00:23:28.907
NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW

294
00:23:28.990 --> 00:23:30.840
Above here leads to the village exit.

295
00:23:31.409 --> 00:23:32.327
Listen. Yuru.

296
00:23:33.286 --> 00:23:37.916
The Divine Guardians Right and Left
will always protect both of you.

